last_run_values: After the breakout from the rectangle on the hourly charts the pair is now testing the support. Stops will be below the range or in this case in the middle of the range. Instead of using the target here we can just use the moving average to ride the trend for as long as possible on the hourly time frame. One can also use the ichimoku for the same
Sell stop order only. Price should move below the marked level, then we might see selling pressure. Never enter early or after the planned trading hours.
